self.process_pcap(os.path.join(saq.SAQ_HOME, 'test_data', 'pcaps',

engine = TestEngine()
engine.start()

collector.load_groups()

wait_for_log_count('found http stream', 1, 5)

engine.controlled_stop()
engine.wait()
collector.stop()
collector.wait()
